</div>
<p>Additional test script specific dependencies could be installed separate=
ly by running the ESP-IDF install script with the <code class=3D"docutils l=
iteral notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">--enable-test-specific</span></code=
> argument:</p>
<div class=3D"highlight-bash notranslate"><div class=3D"highlight"><pre id=
=3D"codecell1"><span></span>$<span class=3D"w"> </span>install.sh<span clas=
s=3D"w"> </span>--enable-test-specific
</pre><button class=3D"copybtn o-tooltip--left" data-tooltip=3D"Copy" data-=
clipboard-target=3D"#codecell1">
      <svg xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class=3D"icon icon-tabler i=
con-tabler-copy" width=3D"44" height=3D"44" viewBox=3D"0 0 24 24" stroke-wi=
dth=3D"1.5" stroke=3D"#000000" fill=3D"none" stroke-linecap=3D"round" strok=
e-linejoin=3D"round">
