</div>
<p>Several mechanisms have been implemented to ensure the successful execut=
ion of the installation processes. If you encounter any issues during insta=
llation, please submit an issue report to our <a class=3D"reference externa=
l" href=3D"https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/issues">GitHub issue tracke=
r</a>.</p>
