</path>
</svg>
    </button></div>
</div>
<p>The <code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">|</=
span></code> symbol in all parameterized items is used for separating the s=
ettings for each DUT. In this example, the test case would be tested with:<=
/p>
<ul class=3D"simple">
<li><p>esp32, esp32s2</p></li>
<li><p>esp32s3, esp32s3</p></li>
</ul>
<p>After setting the param <code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><sp=
an class=3D"pre">count</span></code> to 2, all the fixtures are changed int=
o tuples.</p>
<div class=3D"admonition important">
<p class=3D"admonition-title">Important</p>
