</div>
<div class=3D"admonition note">
<p class=3D"admonition-title">Note</p>
<p>When parametrizing two items, like <code class=3D"docutils literal notra=
nslate"><span class=3D"pre">app_path,</span> <span class=3D"pre">target</sp=
an></code> here, make sure you're passing a list of tuples to the <code cla=
ss=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">parametrize</span><=
/code> decorator. Each tuple should contain the values for each item.</p>
</div>
<p>The test case here will be replicated to 2 test cases:</p>
<ul class=3D"simple">
<li><p>dut-0, an ESP32, running app <code class=3D"docutils literal notrans=
late"><span class=3D"pre">master</span></code>, and dut-1, an ESP32-S2, run=
ning app <code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">s=
lave</span></code></p></li>
<li><p>dut-0, an ESP32-S2, running app <code class=3D"docutils literal notr=
anslate"><span class=3D"pre">master</span></code>, and dut-1, an ESP32, run=
ning app <code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">s=
lave</span></code></p></li>
</ul>
</section>
</section>
<section id=3D"test-cases-with-unity-test-framework">
<h3>Test Cases with Unity Test Framework<a class=3D"headerlink" href=3D"htt=
ps://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/stable/esp32/contribute/esp-idf=
-tests-with-pytest.html#test-cases-with-unity-test-framework" title=3D"Perm=
alink to this heading">=EF=83=81</a></h3>
<p>We use the <a class=3D"reference external" href=3D"https://github.com/Th=
rowTheSwitch/Unity">Unity test framework</a> in our unit tests. Overall, we=
 have three types of test cases (<a class=3D"reference external" href=3D"ht=
tps://github.com/ThrowTheSwitch/Unity">Unity test framework</a>):</p>
<ul class=3D"simple">
<li><p>Normal test cases (single DUT)</p></li>
<li><p>Multi-stage test cases (single DUT)</p></li>
<li><p>Multi-device test cases (multi-DUT)</p></li>
</ul>
<p>All single-DUT test cases (including normal test cases and multi-stage t=
est cases) can be run using the following command:</p>
<div class=3D"highlight-python notranslate"><div class=3D"highlight"><pre i=
d=3D"codecell12"><span></span><span class=3D"k">def</span><span class=3D"w"=
> </span><span class=3D"nf">test_unity_single_dut</span><span class=3D"p">(=
</span><span class=3D"n">dut</span><span class=3D"p">:</span> <span class=
=3D"n">IdfDut</span><span class=3D"p">):</span>
    <span class=3D"n">dut</span><span class=3D"o">.</span><span class=3D"n"=
>run_all_single_board_cases</span><span class=3D"p">()</span>
</pre><button class=3D"copybtn o-tooltip--left" data-tooltip=3D"Copy" data-=
clipboard-target=3D"#codecell12">
      <svg xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class=3D"icon icon-tabler i=
con-tabler-copy" width=3D"44" height=3D"44" viewBox=3D"0 0 24 24" stroke-wi=
dth=3D"1.5" stroke=3D"#000000" fill=3D"none" stroke-linecap=3D"round" strok=
e-linejoin=3D"round">
  <title>Copy to clipboard</title>
  <path stroke=3D"none" d=3D"M0 0h24v24H0z" fill=3D"none"></path>
  <rect x=3D"8" y=3D"8" width=3D"12" height=3D"12" rx=3D"2"></rect>
  <path d=3D"M16 8v-2a2 2 0 0 0 -2 -2h-8a2 2 0 0 0 -2 2v8a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2">=
</path>
</svg>
    </button></div>
</div>
<p>Using this command will skip all the test cases containing the <code cla=
ss=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">[ignore]</span></co=
de> tag.</p>
<p>If you need to run a group of test cases, you may run:</p>
<div class=3D"highlight-python notranslate"><div class=3D"highlight"><pre i=
d=3D"codecell13"><span></span><span class=3D"k">def</span><span class=3D"w"=
> </span><span class=3D"nf">test_unity_single_dut</span><span class=3D"p">(=
</span><span class=3D"n">dut</span><span class=3D"p">:</span> <span class=
=3D"n">IdfDut</span><span class=3D"p">):</span>
    <span class=3D"n">dut</span><span class=3D"o">.</span><span class=3D"n"=
>run_all_single_board_cases</span><span class=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"=
n">group</span><span class=3D"o">=3D</span><span class=3D"s1">'psram'</span=
><span class=3D"p">)</span>
</pre><button class=3D"copybtn o-tooltip--left" data-tooltip=3D"Copy" data-=
clipboard-target=3D"#codecell13">
      <svg xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class=3D"icon icon-tabler i=
con-tabler-copy" width=3D"44" height=3D"44" viewBox=3D"0 0 24 24" stroke-wi=
dth=3D"1.5" stroke=3D"#000000" fill=3D"none" stroke-linecap=3D"round" strok=
e-linejoin=3D"round">
  <title>Copy to clipboard</title>
  <path stroke=3D"none" d=3D"M0 0h24v24H0z" fill=3D"none"></path>
