</path>
</svg>
    </button></div>
</div>
<p>It would trigger all test cases with the <code class=3D"docutils literal=
 notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">[psram]</span></code> tag.</p>
<p>If you need to run all test cases except for a specific groups, you may =
run:</p>
<div class=3D"highlight-python notranslate"><div class=3D"highlight"><pre i=
d=3D"codecell14"><span></span><span class=3D"k">def</span><span class=3D"w"=
> </span><span class=3D"nf">test_unity_single_dut</span><span class=3D"p">(=
</span><span class=3D"n">dut</span><span class=3D"p">:</span> <span class=
=3D"n">IdfDut</span><span class=3D"p">):</span>
    <span class=3D"n">dut</span><span class=3D"o">.</span><span class=3D"n"=
>run_all_single_board_cases</span><span class=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"=
n">group</span><span class=3D"o">=3D</span><span class=3D"s1">'!psram'</spa=
n><span class=3D"p">)</span>
</pre><button class=3D"copybtn o-tooltip--left" data-tooltip=3D"Copy" data-=
clipboard-target=3D"#codecell14">
