</div>
<p>This code will trigger all test cases except those with the [psram] tag.=
</p>
<p>If you need to run a group of test cases filtered by specific attributes=
, you may run:</p>
<div class=3D"highlight-python notranslate"><div class=3D"highlight"><pre i=
d=3D"codecell15"><span></span><span class=3D"k">def</span><span class=3D"w"=
> </span><span class=3D"nf">test_rtc_xtal32k</span><span class=3D"p">(</spa=
n><span class=3D"n">dut</span><span class=3D"p">:</span> <span class=3D"n">=
Dut</span><span class=3D"p">)</span> <span class=3D"o">-&gt;</span> <span c=
lass=3D"kc">None</span><span class=3D"p">:</span>
    <span class=3D"n">dut</span><span class=3D"o">.</span><span class=3D"n"=
>run_all_single_board_cases</span><span class=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"=
n">attributes</span><span class=3D"o">=3D</span><span class=3D"p">{</span><=
span class=3D"s1">'test_env'</span><span class=3D"p">:</span> <span class=
=3D"s1">'xtal32k'</span><span class=3D"p">})</span>
</pre><button class=3D"copybtn o-tooltip--left" data-tooltip=3D"Copy" data-=
clipboard-target=3D"#codecell15">
