con-tabler-copy" width=3D"44" height=3D"44" viewBox=3D"0 0 24 24" stroke-wi=
dth=3D"1.5" stroke=3D"#000000" fill=3D"none" stroke-linecap=3D"round" strok=
e-linejoin=3D"round">
  <title>Copy to clipboard</title>
  <path stroke=3D"none" d=3D"M0 0h24v24H0z" fill=3D"none"></path>
  <rect x=3D"8" y=3D"8" width=3D"12" height=3D"12" rx=3D"2"></rect>
  <path d=3D"M16 8v-2a2 2 0 0 0 -2 -2h-8a2 2 0 0 0 -2 2v8a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2">=
</path>
</svg>
    </button></div>
</div>
<p>This command will trigger all tests with the attribute <code class=3D"do=
cutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">test_env</span></code> equa=
l to <code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">xtal3=
2k</span></code>.</p>
<p>If you need to run tests by specific names, you may run:</p>
<div class=3D"highlight-python notranslate"><div class=3D"highlight"><pre i=
d=3D"codecell16"><span></span><span class=3D"k">def</span><span class=3D"w"=
> </span><span class=3D"nf">test_dut_run_all_single_board_cases</span><span=
 class=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"n">dut</span><span class=3D"p">):</span=
>
    <span class=3D"n">dut</span><span class=3D"o">.</span><span class=3D"n"=
>run_all_single_board_cases</span><span class=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"=
n">name</span><span class=3D"o">=3D</span><span class=3D"p">[</span><span c=
lass=3D"s2">"normal_case1"</span><span class=3D"p">,</span> <span class=3D"=
s2">"multiple_stages_test"</span><span class=3D"p">])</span>
</pre><button class=3D"copybtn o-tooltip--left" data-tooltip=3D"Copy" data-=
