span class=3D"pre">normal_case1</span></code> and <code class=3D"docutils l=
iteral notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">multiple_stages_test</span></code><=
/p>
<p>We also provide a fixture <code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><=
span class=3D"pre">case_tester</span></code> to trigger all kinds of test c=
ases easier. For example:</p>
<div class=3D"highlight-python notranslate"><div class=3D"highlight"><pre i=
d=3D"codecell17"><span></span><span class=3D"k">def</span><span class=3D"w"=
> </span><span class=3D"nf">test_unity_single_dut</span><span class=3D"p">(=
