<section id=3D"mark-known-failures">
<h3>Mark Known Failures<a class=3D"headerlink" href=3D"https://docs.espress=
if.com/projects/esp-idf/en/stable/esp32/contribute/esp-idf-tests-with-pytes=
t.html#mark-known-failures" title=3D"Permalink to this heading">=EF=83=81</=
a></h3>
<p>Sometimes, a test can consistently fail for the following reasons:</p>
<ul class=3D"simple">
<li><p>The feature under test (or the test itself) has a bug.</p></li>
<li><p>The test environment is unstable (e.g., due to network issues) leadi=
ng to a high failure ratio.</p></li>
</ul>
<p>Now you may mark this test case with marker <a class=3D"reference extern=
al" href=3D"https://docs.pytest.org/en/latest/how-to/skipping.html#xfail-ma=
rk-test-functions-as-expected-to-fail">xfail</a> with a user-friendly reada=
ble reason.</p>
<p>This code example is taken from <a class=3D"reference external" href=3D"=
https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/blob/v6.0.2/tools/test_apps/system/pan=
ic/pytest_panic.py">pytest_panic.py </a></p>
<div class=3D"highlight-python notranslate"><div class=3D"highlight"><pre i=
d=3D"codecell28"><span></span><span class=3D"nd">@pytest</span><span class=
=3D"o">.</span><span class=3D"n">mark</span><span class=3D"o">.</span><span=
 class=3D"n">xfail</span><span class=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"s1">'conf=
ig.getvalue("target") =3D=3D "esp32s2"'</span><span class=3D"p">,</span> <s=
pan class=3D"n">reason</span><span class=3D"o">=3D</span><span class=3D"s1"=
>'raised IllegalInstruction instead'</span><span class=3D"p">)</span>
<span class=3D"k">def</span><span class=3D"w"> </span><span class=3D"nf">te=
st_cache_error</span><span class=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"n">dut</span>=
<span class=3D"p">:</span> <span class=3D"n">PanicTestDut</span><span class=
=3D"p">,</span> <span class=3D"n">config</span><span class=3D"p">:</span> <=
span class=3D"nb">str</span><span class=3D"p">,</span> <span class=3D"n">te=
st_func_name</span><span class=3D"p">:</span> <span class=3D"nb">str</span>=
<span class=3D"p">)</span> <span class=3D"o">-&gt;</span> <span class=3D"kc=
">None</span><span class=3D"p">:</span>
</pre><button class=3D"copybtn o-tooltip--left" data-tooltip=3D"Copy" data-=
clipboard-target=3D"#codecell28">
