<section id=3D"mark-nightly-run-test-cases">
<h3>Mark Nightly Run Test Cases<a class=3D"headerlink" href=3D"https://docs=
.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/stable/esp32/contribute/esp-idf-tests-wi=
th-pytest.html#mark-nightly-run-test-cases" title=3D"Permalink to this head=
ing">=EF=83=81</a></h3>
<p>Some test cases are only triggered in nightly run pipelines due to a lac=
k of runners.</p>
