<section id=3D"mark-temporarily-disabled-in-ci">
<h3>Mark Temporarily Disabled in CI<a class=3D"headerlink" href=3D"https://=
docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/stable/esp32/contribute/esp-idf-test=
s-with-pytest.html#mark-temporarily-disabled-in-ci" title=3D"Permalink to t=
his heading">=EF=83=81</a></h3>
<p>Some test cases which can pass locally may need to be temporarily disabl=
ed in CI due to a lack of runners.</p>
<div class=3D"highlight-python notranslate"><div class=3D"highlight"><pre i=
d=3D"codecell30"><span></span><span class=3D"nd">@pytest</span><span class=
=3D"o">.</span><span class=3D"n">mark</span><span class=3D"o">.</span><span=
