l#logging-system" title=3D"Permalink to this heading">=EF=83=81</a></h3>
<p>Sometimes you may need to add some extra logging lines while running the=
 test cases.</p>
<p>You can use <a class=3D"reference external" href=3D"https://docs.python.=
org/3/library/logging.html">Python logging module</a> to achieve this.</p>
<p>Here are some logging functions provided as fixtures,</p>
