rties</span></code> tag in the JUnit report if <code class=3D"docutils lite=
ral notranslate"><span class=3D"pre">--junitxml</span> <span class=3D"pre">=
&lt;filepath&gt;</span></code> is specified. The JUnit test case node would=
 look like:</p>
